snippet.textDisplay: I don't know much about anything else, but I can say one thing even being a patriotic Indian. Pakistan has been blessed with rare talents, rare beauties, rare class, rare elegance, rare music styles. I have played this about 50 times already and still can not get over these two singers. Rahat as always is just pure class, he can be called the Tendulkar of music. Whether it's playback, studio, or live he can win over every heart. The girl is as beautiful as her voice, probably my first "actual" crush hehe. Thank you Pakistan for giving us such breath taking gifts. Keep up the good work! Love and tremendous respect from Ahmedabad :)
